| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0450 — Recovery Inhibition (werewolves)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 841e0f30-36cd-502e-96c7-d4f25a01906c"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
